64
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:34,280
You call him dad, now? How intimate.

65
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:36,320
I don't want to see him. I just care about the money.

66
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:38,880
Transfer it to me now. I'm the one in charge of the money.

67
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:41,720
