68
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,720
No. That's not what we agreed to.

69
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,560
I don't want you wasting 200 euros.

70
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,840
You wanted to read dad the riot act, right?

71
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:50,200
You won. You have what you wanted. So do I.

72
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:53,360
I don't want you to have so much money, damn.

73
