197
00:14:12,680 --> 00:14:15,800
The fact that you talk like that surprises me.

198
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:21,080
No one can tell me how to talk, let alone a kid.

199
00:14:27,560 --> 00:14:29,240
The money is mine and I can do whatever I want.

200
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:30,720
