220
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:13,860
Come on, Toni. I'm not naive.

221
00:16:13,860 --> 00:16:16,400
You know what kind of student Pol is.

222
00:16:16,640 --> 00:16:19,360
And Bruno never gets more than a six. To me, it's very obvious.

223
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:22,290
The father took the exam, gave to his son.

224
00:16:22,290 --> 00:16:23,880
Then, he shared with a friend.

225
00:16:25,880 --> 00:16:28,320
-I don't know. I don't know. -What don't you know?

226
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:37,920
