228
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:46,600
I also think that he may be guilty.

229
00:16:47,040 --> 00:16:49,960
But let's be serious, Eugeni. I will investigate.

230
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:52,640
You will investigate.

231
00:16:56,840 --> 00:17:01,520
